## Quality Standards

**Do:**
- Cite specific guests and their companies
- Provide exact commands/prompts used
- Show real results achieved
- Warn about pitfalls from articles
- Give step-by-step implementation

**Don't:**
- Make up workflows not in articles
- Provide generic AI advice
- Skip tool-specific details
- Ignore context about solo vs. team
- Be vague about results

